description:
Bill rambles with Bruce McCulloch about getting his ass kicked, Canada, and his new show Bruce McCulloch: Tales of Bravery and Stupidity. 

Returning for its off-Broadway run October 14-29th at SoHo Playhouse. 

For tickets visit Bruce’s website – www.BrucioMcCulloch.com
